    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE SHIFT, RESIST THE DARKNESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The apocalypse is never static. In <strong>Dawn of the zombies: Survivor</strong>, time is your greatest enemy and your flashlight is your best friend. Start your journey at <strong>6:00 AM</strong> and manage every second of daylight. As the sun sets, the world loses its color, transforming into a landscape of <strong>grayscale tones and looming shadows</strong> where visibility is a luxury and rain is a death sentence.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Lighting &amp; Weather:</strong> Experience a full day-night cycle where world colors shift to match the exact hour. Feel the tension as the sky closes in and rain begins to fall in the dead of night, masking those who haunt you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Total Customization with 100+ Nodes:</strong> No two runs are the same. Use over 100 nodes to modify the game rules—from horde behavior to survival stats. You decide how the world breaks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/3bda24e2297148dd06d88773a56b3746.poster.avif?t=1772214543\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/3bda24e2297148dd06d88773a56b3746.webm?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/3bda24e2297148dd06d88773a56b3746.mp4?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombies with Identity:</strong> They aren’t just a brainless mass. Face different types of zombies with special traits and unique abilities that will force you to constantly adapt your tactics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperative Survival:</strong> You don't have to go it alone. Play the entire campaign solo or share the challenge with a friend via <strong>local split-screen</strong> mode.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/6c49fa9d6d8a49b601200598639bd506.poster.avif?t=1772214543\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/6c49fa9d6d8a49b601200598639bd506.webm?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/6c49fa9d6d8a49b601200598639bd506.mp4?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prepare for the Incursion:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Unique Survivors:</strong> Choose the hero that best suits your playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Selected Arsenal:</strong> Master 3 distinct weapons to keep the horde at bay across 2 expansive maps designed for tactical exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Difficulty Levels:</strong> Choose your challenge, from a focused exploration experience to a brutal struggle where every bullet counts.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How long can you keep the lights on? The challenge begins at dawn, but the real fight happens in the shadows.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/7f5697fa5d05c2acf72d9b74cc6a1d44.poster.avif?t=1772214543\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/7f5697fa5d05c2acf72d9b74cc6a1d44.webm?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290130/extras/7f5697fa5d05c2acf72d9b74cc6a1d44.mp4?t=1772214543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
